  <h1><span>October 1, 1990: Address to the United Nations</span>
</h1>


    <div class="share-trigger-mobile"></div>
</div>
<div id="block-mainpagecontent">
  
    
      <article role="article" class="presidential-speech">

  
    

  <div class="ps-container video-container">
    <div class="presidential-speeches--sidebar">
      
<div  class="about-this-episode">
    <h3>About this speech</h3>
      
<div  class="about-this-episode--inner">
      
            <p class="president-name">George H. W. Bush</p>
      
            <p class="episode-date">October 01, 1990</p>
      
  <div class="speech-location-container">
    <span class="speech-label">Location</span>
              <span class="speech-loc">National Archives</span>
          </div>

            <div class="about-sidebar--intro"><p>Bush emphasizes the need for a stronger United Nations in the post-Cold War era. He also highlights the importance of free elections and action against Iraq.</p>
</div>
      
  </div>
  </div>
    </div>

    <div class="presidential-speeches--body-wrapper">
     <a href="/the-presidency/presidential-speeches" class="back-to-listing--cta">Presidential Speeches</a> <span class="nav-separator">|</span> <label class="presidential-speeches--label">George H. W. Bush Presidency</label>
      <h2 class="presidential-speeches--title"><span>October 1, 1990: Address to the United Nations</span>
</h2>
      
<div  class="presidential-speeches--body">
      
            <div class="presidential-speeches--audio"><div class="audio-player">
    <audio height="100" src="https://web2.millercenter.org/speeches/audio/spe_1990_1001_bush.mp3"
                            data-wave_color="#888888"
                                        data-prog_color="#E65400"
                            ></audio>
